  <brief_title>Sodium Bicarbonate Versus Saline for the Prevention of Contrast-induced Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Sodium Bicarbonate Versus Saline for the Prevention of Contrast-induced Nephropathy in Patients Undergoing Coronary Angiography</official_title>
  <sponsors>
